title: PLEASE READ
author: benster56
pages:
#- Hello Irians!  This is a message from the Hjaltland Department of Trade, and its Minister of Trade, benster56.  I am trying to increase trade/relationships in this region with the help of our railsystem.  I am sending this in hopes of reaching wolfeyes to
#- see what items of abundance you have, and what you lack.  I hope to become close allies in trade!  Please send back a book with a small list of things you have and what you don't.  Also send one back if you refuse to trade, so I can be more efficient.  
#- Thank you!

Sincerely,
benster56, Hjaltland Minister of Trade
#- 